<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="III"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="III (Find Yourself)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Athletics"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Who You Are Is Not Enough"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="853411964"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="853412051"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3947467"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="31370542"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="3BHlOb4aOdaMaIfJ4M13RP"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5g7CeADGtNZkyu9R99yuI1"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001nbBvC2Lw6cA"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="0046UuID2NXw5X"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="171883270"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="lansogame"/></metadata></head><body dur="6:10.435"><div begin="57.071" end="6:10.435"><p begin="57.071" end="1:10.217" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.071" end="57.300">I</span> <span begin="57.300" end="57.981">read</span> <span begin="57.981" end="58.304">your</span> <span begin="58.304" end="59.039">note,</span> <span begin="1:00.819" end="1:01.125">and</span> <span begin="1:01.125" end="1:02.117">I</span> <span begin="1:02.117" end="1:03.533">know</span> <span begin="1:04.756" end="1:05.182">just</span> <span begin="1:05.182" end="1:06.138">what</span> <span begin="1:06.138" end="1:06.530">you</span> <span begin="1:06.530" end="1:07.709">want</span> <span begin="1:07.709" end="1:08.143">to</span> <span begin="1:08.143" end="1:09.345">hear.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我读了你留下的便签，心中明了你想要的回答</span></p><p begin="1:10.197" end="1:20.417" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.197" end="1:10.393">It</span> <span begin="1:10.393" end="1:10.791">hurts</span> <span begin="1:10.791" end="1:11.281">less</span> <span begin="1:11.281" end="1:11.889">over</span> <span begin="1:11.889" end="1:12.935">time,</span> <span begin="1:13.625" end="1:13.809">but</span> <span begin="1:13.809" end="1:14.239">I’m</span> <span begin="1:14.239" end="1:14.612">not</span> <span begin="1:14.612" end="1:15.277">getting</span> <span begin="1:15.277" end="1:16.124">stronger.</span> <span begin="1:16.124" end="1:16.804">I</span> <span begin="1:16.804" end="1:17.225">just</span> <span begin="1:17.225" end="1:17.682">leave</span> <span begin="1:17.682" end="1:18.513">pieces</span> <span begin="1:18.513" end="1:19.528">behind.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">时间能治愈伤痛，但这并不代表我会更坚强，我只会留下回忆的碎片</span></p><p begin="1:20.417" end="2:04.966" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.417" end="1:20.612">And</span> <span begin="1:20.612" end="1:21.023">I</span> <span begin="1:21.023" end="1:21.242">can</span> <span begin="1:21.242" end="1:22.345">only</span> <span begin="1:22.345" end="1:23.206">fall</span> <span begin="1:23.206" end="1:24.073">so</span> <span begin="1:24.073" end="1:25.361">many</span> <span begin="1:25.361" end="1:27.432">times</span> <span begin="1:28.017" end="1:28.834">before</span> <span begin="1:28.834" end="1:29.743">I’m</span> <span begin="1:29.743" end="1:30.975">broke,</span> <span begin="1:32.306" end="1:32.704">un</span><span begin="1:32.704" end="1:33.559">re</span><span begin="1:33.559" end="1:33.956">cog</span><span begin="1:33.956" end="1:35.184">ni</span><span begin="1:35.184" end="1:35.651">za</span><span begin="1:35.651" end="1:36.176">ble.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">等我多次落寞，物是人非之后，我只会更加堕落</span></p><p begin="2:04.966" end="2:22.337" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.966" end="2:05.189">Now</span> <span begin="2:05.189" end="2:05.628">all</span> <span begin="2:05.628" end="2:06.017">I’ve</span> <span begin="2:06.017" end="2:06.509">left</span> <span begin="2:06.509" end="2:06.781">to</span> <span begin="2:06.781" end="2:07.701">give</span> <span begin="2:09.477" end="2:09.920">is</span> <span begin="2:09.920" end="2:10.341">the</span> <span begin="2:10.341" end="2:11.206">piece</span> <span begin="2:11.206" end="2:11.557">that</span> <span begin="2:11.557" end="2:12.957">still</span> <span begin="2:12.957" end="2:13.849">remains,</span> <span begin="2:18.401" end="2:18.661">and</span> <span begin="2:18.661" end="2:18.935">you</span> <span begin="2:18.935" end="2:19.412">bring</span> <span begin="2:19.412" end="2:19.629">the</span> <span begin="2:19.629" end="2:21.055">pieces</span> <span begin="2:21.055" end="2:21.893">back.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我留给你的那段时光 仍历历在目 你将其唤醒</span></p><p begin="2:22.337" end="2:32.189" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.337" end="2:22.789">Love,</span> <span begin="2:22.789" end="2:23.224">it</span> <span begin="2:23.224" end="2:24.117">only</span> <span begin="2:24.117" end="2:24.913">re</span><span begin="2:24.913" end="2:25.364">con</span><span begin="2:25.364" end="2:26.609">structs</span> <span begin="2:26.609" end="2:27.097">the</span> <span begin="2:27.097" end="2:28.405">pain.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所谓的爱，只会唤起伤痛</span></p><p begin="2:32.189" end="2:45.930" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:32.189" end="2:32.602">As</span> <span begin="2:32.602" end="2:33.029">time</span> <span begin="2:33.029" end="2:33.484">fails</span> <span begin="2:33.484" end="2:33.981">to</span> <span begin="2:33.981" end="2:35.696">elapse,</span> <span begin="2:35.696" end="2:36.144">I’m</span> <span begin="2:36.144" end="2:36.956">finding</span> <span begin="2:36.956" end="2:37.369">you</span> <span begin="2:37.369" end="2:37.859">were</span> <span begin="2:37.859" end="2:38.685">eve</span><span begin="2:38.685" end="2:39.070">ry</span><span begin="2:39.070" end="2:40.386">thing</span> <span begin="2:40.386" end="2:40.827">to</span> <span begin="2:40.827" end="2:42.083">me.</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无法逃脱的宿命，我发现你是我的一切</span></p><p begin="2:45.920" end="6:10.435" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.920" end="2:46.137">Now</span> <span begin="2:46.137" end="2:46.340">my</span> <span begin="2:46.340" end="2:47.033">future</span> <span begin="2:47.033" end="2:47.453">and</span> <span begin="2:47.453" end="2:47.943">my</span> <span begin="2:47.943" end="2:50.203">past</span> <span begin="2:50.203" end="2:50.652">are</span> <span begin="2:50.652" end="2:51.541">ending</span> <span begin="2:51.541" end="2:52.367">tra</span><span begin="2:52.367" end="2:52.822">gi</span><span begin="2:52.822" end="2:54.131">cally</span> <span begin="2:54.131" end="2:54.544">the</span> <span begin="2:54.544" end="2:58.324">same</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但如今我的未来和过往 终将以同样的悲剧收场</span></p></div></body></tt>